snippet.textDisplay:
Ok, this looks amazing. Those new Galarian legendary birds! New Regis! Slowpoke and the other pokemon being allowed back into Galar! Cool new legendary pokemon that we get to train with and adventure for (as it should be!) Open world areas with little to no hand holding! Sweet looking Gigantimax forms for the starters new and old! Plus a bunch of new outfits! I preordered this without hesitation! (Really hope there's a Team Magma outfit.)

Now if I could just find a shiny Wooloo and get past Route 1, I'll be set.
